{"tid":1461943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔好分化］機場策略","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:42.000Z","uid":135472,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"26b4c0459137502cf9a084bb129f48e672894e37","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"和理非嘅 宣傳嘅就去arrival 唔好阻人<br />\n不合作嘅 阻物流門口 香港物流都賺唔少"},{"pid":"5174aae7ddbb748d362254bbcb27dde8388ca36a","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1599fad6a2d93412d818c961f5f0d3116d81643b","tid":1461943,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"3d00100aaca5f4659528dca5955023bce6b9e77b","tid":1461943,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d88b7115d1aee3344dcc564e26b541a7cd8448c7","tid":1461943,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"推 一般旅客對香港經濟有咩影響 對政府有咩壓力<br />\n要阻去阻貨機"},{"pid":"49e9a3564ff38da9ef2f6c79d7b3c5c211f1a633","tid":1461943,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"好撚肯定傳停飛果班，唔係狗就係弱智<br />\n<br />\n成個下午都唔停<br />\n偏偏收工時間先嚟停，為乜？<br />\n等你班撚樣見做咗成日嘢，攰攰地，就諗住停飛咗所以返屋企抖，然後無人入去<br />\n<br />\n你老闆，尋日係咁，今日又係咁，醒未呀！<br />\n入機場啦<br />\n轉頭過咗收工時間，復飛又無人岀<br />\n然後旅客又怪落班示威者度<br />\n<br />\n叫大家傳開去<br />\nP牌仔今日開咗post ，無得再開<br />\n一定要入機場"},{"pid":"c1337cbd234a8b561b36948e2c01ba17e2e87dd1","tid":1461943,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:46:03.000Z","msg":"比旅客過 留返條路 機場停咗係政府自己停<br />\n唔需要100%癱瘓, 最理想係 70% Cancel<br />\n100%癱瘓=無服務=無遊客旅客無職員<br />\n黑警到時落閘放狗, 瘋狂掃射<br />\n<br />\n機場係持久戰! <br />\n勇武退場 世界文宣!<br />\n<br />\n香港人，我地有能力攬炒全球！<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;m not saying the protesters are playing with fire. I think the protesters want fire&rdquo;"},{"pid":"df908a524353146c604808f1dc4522aa4647b9be","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意氣用事 之前機場宣傳贏咗唔少民意 依家好容易被人抹黑"},{"pid":"6a801b13b68d5ff58ebdf192acda4c172b8da8c5","tid":1461943,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"agger 阻物流 但點阻"},{"pid":"e8960ba8c13bc7d6de8ff576f410183c9d8121c1","tid":1461943,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"機場唔夠人，罷唔到工嘅手足自己組隊輪流請假去啦<br />\n只要搵到20萬人係一星期內肯請一日假, 每日有4萬人<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDjHuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDjHuS</a>"},{"pid":"36402a6b90f545b85e29c4e3f029e290996cb46d","tid":1461943,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"5fd145c5ea4ec14e65632a7083e8f85aa2874ebc","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a801b13b68d5ff58ebdf192acda4c172b8da8c5","tid":1461943,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"agger 阻物流 但點阻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"駿裕路"},{"pid":"11e3cde297baf84f9b66ebe6744192ccc85f8d5c","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"尋日係阻人上機 但係係hkaa阻人上機 唔係我哋"},{"pid":"0497e8c4e77236366ef7a9730ed51606c3db272b","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"唔好心急"},{"pid":"19a34a6a7ce2f97f07022d2f47e1e2ec92b57eaf","tid":1461943,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"旅客係用來保護機場示威者，你要攪唔該出去搞警署狗屋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"012eea59289a8f422732e9ccd21299f732bf2bf5","tid":1461943,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<br />\n借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如分化、恐慌、煽動、造謠等等）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"fed57992668a76f7aae2c85119c972295f07944d","tid":1461943,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df908a524353146c604808f1dc4522aa4647b9be","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意氣用事 之前機場宣傳贏咗唔少民意 依家好容易被人抹黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=00d49c53\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again</a>"},{"pid":"a7850089f5644421512fb14c0ef4e6f844ae1e34","tid":1461943,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"謝絕破壞，不使用武力!"},{"pid":"81f54bd0eb69a4403e0f0eed2ce3efe46f5c8362","tid":1461943,"uid":129021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"係時候打電話煩航空公司扮乘客問應唔應該出門口。表達好不滿，將責任賴晒落航空公司度，令航空公司向機管局施壓盡快關閉機場。"},{"pid":"c947b9413755a305b67f5883bdf3894a3a044f0e","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1260d2ec676a8cec6b16e033d7f148a710a64372","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"079351d93d2751a9aebf9638bc44800bbf489e3f","tid":1461943,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"６１２ ７２１ ８１１！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ed491e1fde802b5714c304123e99197639982e","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"塞鐵都可以話阻人翻工可以影響經濟<br />\n但係直接阻人上機咩都做唔到<br />\n直接阻人上機<br />\n1 唔會取消航班<br />\n2 令遊客反感<br />\n3 HKAA唔洗賠錢<br />\n4 政府會放大抹黑<br />\n尋日係因為交通塞所以成功<br />\n巴絲唔好意氣用事"},{"pid":"cb0e22895dff68afbbd3106c3d7f3479aa60bcd4","tid":1461943,"uid":135472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d840bc284939baf4e7ff3c198660cddfb56acfb2","tid":1461943,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過策略應該係塞機場交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迫爆機鐵 各區巴士<br />\n自然會有琴日好難入機場嘅狀況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}